    <string name="about1">Zazen Meditation Timer — Moslashtiriladigan bo\'limlar, qo\'ng\'iroq tovushlari va seanslarni boshqarish imkoniyatiga ega oddiy meditatsiya taymeri.</string>
    <string name="about2">Aslida Stefan Gaffga tomonidan yaratilgan. Hozirda Georg Graf tomonidan qo\'llab-quvvatlanmoqda.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ajoyib qo\'ng\'iroq tovushlari uchun &lt;a href="http://www.meditationsuhren.de">http://www.meditationsuhren.de&lt;/a&gt; saytidan Winfriedga minnatdorchilik bildiramiz!</string>
    <string name="about3">&lt;a href="https://github.com/georgernstgraf/zazentimer/issues">GitHub orqali xatoliklar haqida xabar berish&lt;/a&gt;</string>
